## 💡 Recommendations for User

1. [Recommendation based on findings]
2. [Suggestion for next /auto-evolve run]
```

### 4.2. Update Session

Update `.brain/session.json`:
- `working_on`: auto-evolve session
- `recent_changes`: add entry

