## 📝 Auto-Save Lesson

After evolution run, if notable patterns or recurring issues found:
1. Check `.brain/lessons.md` exists (if not → create from template)
2. Write to "## Recent" section:
   ```
   ### [Date] - /auto-evolve - [Context]
   - ✅ Fixed: [Summary of successful improvements]
   - 🔄 Deferred: [Items for user review]
   - 📁 Branch: auto-evolve/[date]
   ```

